data.description: Welcome to 249 Hog Eye Rd, a custom-built 4-bed, 2-bath layout on over half an acre. The home features luxurious plank vinyl flooring throughout, adding a touch of sophistication and easy maintenance to every corner, and a meticulously designed kitchen with all stainless steel appliances. The primary suite is a haven of relaxation, boasting a custom tile shower and a spa-like bathroom, complete with a rejuvenating soaking tub. Each of the four bedrooms is generously sized providing ample room for personal comfort. In addition to the main residence, a detached 20 x 24 shop with electricity, wired with a 30 amp receptacle for an RV, and a 50 amp for a welder, all on a separate electric box. The expansive lot provides a blank canvas for outdoor activities, gardening, or creating your dream outdoor space. Nestled in Potosi Prairie, this property provides the best of both worlds, a tranquil retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life while still being conveniently close to town.
